PrecisAppointment of RENÉE COLLETTE, of Laval, Quebec, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period of five years; and designation of the said RENÉE COLLETTE as the Executive Vice-Chairperson of the National Parole Board to hold office during pleasure; effective March 17, 1997.
